Create an Einstein Bot Template

Required Editions: Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, Developer
User Permissions Needed: Customize Application, Modify Metadata, Manage Bots

To create a template: 
  Go to the Templates tab in the Einstein Bots main page.
  Click New and specify the template name, primary language, secondary languages, and bot type.
  Optionally add a permission set for access to required resources.
  Update the welcome message and add menu items as needed.
  Confirm the finishing touches and click Finish.
